title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update IX Italy & Malta - Parma
description:
In this video we will have a look at Parma which has received a photogrammetry update as part of World Update IX. Compared to other cities the city of Parma didn't receive a lot of additional objects such as POI's however the photogrammetry content is still impressive to see.
